sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant Client as React Client
  participant Store as Redux Store
  participant API as Express API
  participant DB as SQLite via TypeORM

  User->>Client: Click Fetch
  Client->>Store: fetchRandomPeople
  Store-->>Client: randomPeople
  User->>Client: Open profile
  User->>Client: Click Save
  Client->>Store: savePerson
  Store->>API: POST /api/people
  API->>DB: repository.save
  DB-->>API: saved profile
  API-->>Store: saved profile
  Store-->>Client: update savedPeople
